OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day and cloudy
OL,6,Fat times with sunny spells. Mostly
OL,7,Fcloudy in the morning with some longer
OL,8,Fsunny spells developing through the
OL,9,Fcourse of the day. Warm in the
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with plenty of
OL,13,Flate evening sunshine on offer, but
OL,14,Fcloudier in the east. Remaining dry
OL,15,Fovernight with long clear spells in
OL,16,Fthe west but cloudier in east.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FA dry day with occasional
OL,19,Fcloud and plenty of long sunny spells.
OL,20,FA warmer day than Monday for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
